window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Five months there. Five months back. And seven months waiting for the planets to align. </p> <p>In a tiny ship never meant for deep space, Denali is one hell of a trip. But the leading mind in nanite medicine is stranded there. Captain Sass Collier wants him back, to cure failure to thrive syndrome in her own colony. </p> <p>Each of the crew has a motive to embrace the risk. The lucky ones wish for adventure. Adventure is assured. But Denali holds another prize beyond their wildest dreams. </p> <p>Can Sass hold her fractious crew together, get the goods, and meet her launch window home? </p> <p>Pick up Thrive Publisher Packs because you love a rollicking space opera with heart! Contains books 3 and 4 in the Thrive Space Colony Adventures: </p> <p>3. <i>Interplanetary Thrive</i> - Tedium and terror on the voyage to Denali.</p> <p>4. <i>Starship Thrive</i> - Wonder and discovery on the hothouse planet. </p> <p>This concludes the first season arc of Thriveâ€”the Aloha home star system.</p>"; 
